---
title: Bacon & Mushroom Risotto with Leafy Cucumber Salad
description: Finishing tonight's risotto in the oven means minimal elbow work, and maximum flavour, with the starchy, short grain rice
soaking up the salty, umami-rich bacon and meaty mushrooms like a treat. Stir through the Parmesan cheese once the risotto is
done for a subtly sharp and tangy depth of flavour.
